          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Community forum access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm">3 basic tutorials per month</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Public project collaborations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start opacity-50">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 mr-2"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Advanced AI tools</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start opacity-50">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 mr-2"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Premium courses</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#join" class={buttonVariants({ variant: "outline", size: "lg", className: "w-full" })}>
            Get Started
